ce and the underlying spot index. The funding rate is determined by the 8-hour time-weighted average premium, with payments occurring every hour between long and short position holders. dYdX's Cosmos appchain architecture ensures transparent on-chain settlement of all funding payments."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
